content: Lydia English is a graduate research assistant in the department of Agronomy at Iowa State University. She currently works for Dr. Matt Liebman. She is interested in diversifying agricultural landscapes by extending crop rotations and incorporating native habitat into farmscapes. She is affiliated with the STRIPS project at Iowa State University.
